נשׁים    - אשּׁה / 'ishshâh  - nâshîym / ish-shaw', naw-sheem'
=== Etymology ===

The first form is the feminine of H376 or H582; 
the second form is an irregular plural; 
=== Noun ===
a woman (used in the same wide sense as H582).: - [adulter]ess, each, every, female, X many, + none, one, + together, wife, woman. Often unexpressed in English.